name: San Fernando Hill - Trinidad and Tobago, West Indies, 2021
description: The view from the absolute peak of San Fernando Hill in the island nation of Trinidad, taken mid-2021 while the country was under lockdown due to the COVID pandemic. The streets are rarely ever this empty, and the sky is clear as the oil refining plants are temporarily shut down. This makes this a possibly once-in-a-lifetime snapshot of the country at rest, before regular activity resumed.
